b: ^Represents Death, a letter that inspires fear
^But wrongly because on the contrary, it is life in its purest sense
^It is believed, in fact, the total renewal at the end of any chapter of life
^And is that bad or is it good?
^I did not say that someone is going to die here
^Just say that something in your life is going to change
^Something unforeseen, from a facet of your life that until now you have neglected a lot
^Unsafe and dangerous travel, panic, confusion and even ruin
^But if that's exactly what I do, travel
^What are you telling me I'm going to be like this forever?
^Uncertain trips are, but that doesn't mean they are forever
^For a person who lives in a city it may mean that a move is coming
^But for someone nomadic like you, it may mean that the next trip may be the last
^Either because something will stop you or because of death itself
^But I would dare to say that it will be due to a person ...
^Why does everyone ask if the cards are bad and not, if they are good?
^The Star means Bright Prospects, success and friendly help, prosperity and revelations
^A passive and generous fortune, beauty and romance
^It may be that one of them happens to you or maybe all of them, but something is certain a new path will open before you
^The star will guide you through it, but it will be you who chooses it
^The path of generosity, where your assets are exchanged for love, closeness and friendship
^Or greed, full of goods and material prosperity
^In short, what he feared, the Sword.
^What's up with that, should I buy one?
^It means the price to pay, resignation, repentance, ecstasy and forced punishment
^Egocentricity and illusions, harmful habits seasoned by anguish and fear
^You should already know what happens with that because if I'm not wrong
^It means that you run away from something and that you are going to regret
^Or that you are forcing yourself to run away, as punishment for something you think is your fault.
^Mmm ... interesting without a doubt, you have come out of La Luna
^Because it means hidden, hidden dangers, fantastic imagination
^Error and bad influence, lies, indolence, secrets and lunatic people
^That means that your decisions take you in ways that should not
^And not for the better, that is why you are looking for a new meaning to your future because you want to run away from it.
^But you're not going to run away because your decisions lead you straight back to him, to your mistakes, to your regret, to your condemnation.
^An advice? Don't run away anymore, face it and you will stop running away from it, you will be free.
^Positive meaning of triumph and reward, total realization
^Security and achievement of the highest aspirations, lasting success
^Reward for hard work, growth and strength
^Without a doubt the best of the cards without possible misinterpretation.
^You come looking for something and you will find it, your path comes to an end you can rest and feel free.
